<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm von Wolfstein zu Sulzbürg</head><p>Der Rat bittet Wilhelm von Wolfstein um Anweisung des Ulrich Schwarz, Richter zu Pyrbaum, die zwei Ochsen des Heinz Pesold von Lindelburg, Armmann des Klarissenklosters zu Nürnberg, herauszugeben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_260" id="129v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_260_r2l18">VVılhelm vom vvolfſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l19">cʒu der Salcʒpürg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l20"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> / Als vvir euch vor
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd den
                                <expan>heincʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> huber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener cʒu euch geſant
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des heincʒen peſolts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l22">von Lintelberg <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                        hinter dem Cloſter hie cʒu ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l23">Claren ſicʒt das vns cʒu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſtet / vnd dem ewr
                        Rihter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l24">cʒu Pirbaum der Swarcʒ Vlrich auf das ſein geriten
                        vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l25">Jm cʒwen Ochſen <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat /
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr
                            <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l26">Rihter daran vveẏſen vnd auch mit Jm ſchicken vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l27"><expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllet / daʒ Er
                        dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>heincʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> peſolt <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l28">ſein Ochſen widerker / Als etc / das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan></del>
<expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r2l29"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan>
<expan>walpurg<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_260" id="129v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm vom Wolfstein czu der Salczpürg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>, als wir euch vor
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den
                                <expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Huber,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, czu euch gesant
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des Heinczen Pesolts von
                        Lintelberg <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, der hinter dem closter hie czu
                        sant Claren siczt, das uns czu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        stet, und dem ewr rihter czu Pirbaum, der Swarcz Ulrich, auf das sein
                        geriten und im czwen ochsen <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat,
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> rihter daran weysen und auch mit im schicken
                        und <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz er dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Pesolt <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sein ochsen widerker. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Walpurg<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
